{"tid":1464910,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"停止分化，免重蹈14年覆轍","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:40:46.000Z","uid":5967,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fd1a5a4aaa06952837452935835ba54e7763ec5c","tid":1464910,"uid":5967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:35:48.000Z","msg":"立即停止分化<br />\n記唔記得2014年點輸？<br />\n<br />\n衝就係鬼<br />\n守就係鬼<br />\n拆大台就鬼<br />\n起大台就鬼<br />\n<br />\n而家機場要避免重新變成金鐘comfort zone 既盲點<br />\n<br />\n同時要打破思想盲點<br />\n停止再用勇武同和理分類手足<br />\n<br />\n衝立會既手足，可以今晚選擇去靜坐唔圍狗<br />\n同樣坐左4日既手足，可能突然火遮眼，出去打狗，圍狗<br />\n<br />\n咁以上既手足，你應該稱呼佢係勇武定係和理？<br />\n<br />\n突破思想盲點，停止限制自己角色<br />\n<br />\n你今日係和理，聽日可以係勇武<br />\n<br />\n停止切割，停止分化<br />\n<br />\n保護手足<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n黑警，以眼還眼"},{"pid":"b3ab43dd793199d3dfd4a75d9b2ec556ef80b760","tid":1464910,"uid":5967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:38:35.000Z","msg":"立即推"},{"pid":"3a42ffcc62f2f649050de57267e7d52b1151a9e0","tid":1464910,"uid":30367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:40:36.000Z","msg":"Agree， 推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593a2837777425fc93dcb1ed1959ab581fd2d77e","tid":1464910,"uid":5967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:42:56.000Z","msg":"立即推"},{"pid":"c4f79b168c83852c4a3cdb6766df26eeddbad23a","tid":1464910,"uid":70397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c0be426fb0b7427e75fac88e7f491189a7633e","tid":1464910,"uid":5967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:44:42.000Z","msg":"唔好亂捉鬼<br />\n如果佢係幫我地衝立會既手足<br />\n<br />\n你今日捉左佢<br />\n交左人，咁姐係點？"},{"pid":"1de93baeda0eeda0f44e3e64dfec669bcfb28692","tid":1464910,"uid":48870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2